1. The study was conducted between April 7, 2008, and Nov 29, 2013.
2. A total of 547 patients were enrolled in the study.
3. The patients were randomly assigned to different treatment groups.
4. One group was assigned to receive twice-daily concurrent chemoradiotherapy.
5. The twice-daily concurrent chemoradiotherapy group consisted of 274 patients.
6. Another group was assigned to receive once-daily concurrent chemoradiotherapy.
7. The once-daily concurrent chemoradiotherapy group consisted of 273 patients.
